%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fraveena-tandons-daughter-rasha-thadanis-reaction-to-being-photographed-by-paparazzi%2Farticleshow%2F106997862.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Czech%20High%20Court%20Allows%20Nikhil%20Gupta's%20Extradition%20to%20the%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20004338%2FPrague-court.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Czech%20Republic%E2%80%99s%20High%20Court%20in%20Prague%20has%20given%20the%20green%20light%20for%20the%20extradition%20of%20Indian%20national%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20to%20the%20United%20States%20to%20face%20%E2%80%98murder-for-hire%E2%80%99%20charges%20in%20the%20alleged%20conspiracy%20to%20kill%20a%20Khalistani%20activist%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20an%20Indian%20government%20official.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Czech%20justice%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Vladimir%20Repka%20confirmed%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20High%20Court%20had%20ruled%20that%20Gupta%20could%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20High%20Court%20of%20Prague%20has%20ruled%20that%20extradition%20is%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20date%20of%20the%20ruling%20has%20not%20been%20made%20public%2C%20the%20order%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERepka%20said%20that%20the%20process%20would%20move%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20if%20there%20is%20an%20appeal.%20Even%20if%20there%20is%20no%20appeal%20now%20or%20if%20there%20are%20further%20proceedings%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20final%20decision%20on%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20extradition%20will%20be%20made%20by%20the%20justice%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20case%20will%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Justice.%20Minister%20of%20Justice%20Pavel%20Blazek%20will%20decide%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20allow%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20extradition%20to%20the%20US%20at%20a%20later%20date%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERepka%20said%20minister%20Blazek%20had%20a%20period%20of%20three%20months%20to%20ask%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20review%20its%20decision%20%E2%80%9Cif%20the%20Minister%20of%20Justice%20has%20doubts%20about%20the%20correctness%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20in%20a%20given%20matter%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20it%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cimpossible%20to%20predict%20when%20the%20minister%20will%20make%20a%20decision%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20requested%20party%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20use%20all%20available%20means%20to%20prevent%20extradition%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Repka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%2C%20who%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20Delhi%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20June%2030%2C%202023%20at%20the%20Czech%20Republic%E2%80%99s%20Vaclav%20Havel%20airport%20upon%20arriving%20on%20a%20flight%20from%20India%20and%20after%20an%20initial%20request%20from%20the%20US%20based%20on%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20issued%20on%20June%2013.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20sent%20a%20formal%20request%20for%20extradition%20to%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20in%20August%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20sealed%20indictment%20against%20Gupta%20had%20been%20filed%20earlier%20at%20a%20federal%20court%20in%20New%20York%2C%20but%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20name%20only%20became%20public%20after%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20released%20the%20new%20detailed%20charges%20in%20Novemb