%20the%20Home%20Ministry.%20We%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%2C%20except%20to%20look%20after%20the%20people%20who%20are%20staying%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Mizoram%20Chief%20Minister%20who%20defeated%20Zoramthanga%20of%20the%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%20in%20the%20recent%20assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fjfbr8l5g_n-biren-singh-chandel_625x300_15_January_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2012%2C%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20had%20asked%20his%20Mizoram%20counterpart%20Lalduhoma%20not%20to%20interfere%20in%20the%20internal%20matters%20of%20Manipur%2C%20but%20rather%20give%20support%20in%20restoring%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20comments%20by%20Lalduhoma%20on%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20tension%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20had%20said%20Lalduhoma%20must%20stop%20expressing%20views%20that%20are%20beyond%20his%20constitutional%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20A%20lot%20of%20communities%20have%20been%20living%20in%20(border%20town)%20Moreh.%20My%20earnest%20appeal%20to%20him%20is%2C%20please%20help%20us%20restore%20peace.%20I%20never%20commented%20when%20the%20Bru%20issue%20happened%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20so%20please%20pray%20and%20help%20us%20restore%20normalcy%20in%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20had%20said%20at%20an%20event%20in%20the%20honour%20of%20Nupi%20Lan%20(Women's%20War)%2C%20a%20key%20historical%20event%20when%20the%20women%20of%20Manipur%20fought%20against%20the%20British%20twice%20-%20in%201904%20and%201939.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bru%20tribes%20have%20been%20living%20in%20relief%20camps%20in%