quot%3BI%20was%20working%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20cricket%20but%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20for%20us%20to%20work%20in%20this%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ashraf%20chief%20as%20quoted%20by%20the%20news%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20it%20is%20up%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20%5BAnwaar-ul-Haq%20Kakar%5D%2C%20whomever%20he%20nominates%20%5Bwill%20take%20my%20place%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20of%20Zaka%20Ashraf's%20resignation%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20Mickey%20Arthur%2C%20Grant%20Bradburn%20and%20Andrew%20Puttick%20quit%20their%20respective%20positions%20at%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%20(NCA)%20in%20Lahore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Pakistan%20failed%20to%20accomplish%20any%20big%20crown%20since%20Zaka%20Ashraf's%20appointment%20last%20year.%20The%20team%20failed%20to%20reach%20for%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20final%20and%20was%20later%20knocked%20out%20from%20the%20league%20stages%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20World%20Cup%20debacle%2C%20Babar%20Azam%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20captaincy%20and%20was%20succeeded%20by%20Shan%20Masood%20(Test)%20and%20Shaheen%20Afridi%20(T20I).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20captain%20Mohammad%20Hafeez%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20Pakistan%20team%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20ANI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705684200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fi9qlpo4_zaka-ashraf-twitter_625x300_22_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbig-shock-in-pakistan-cricket-frustrated-pcb-chairman-zaka-ashraf-quits-says-not-possible-to-work-4894882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20chairman%20Zaka%20Ashraf%20has%20stepped%20down%20from%20his%20role.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prem%20Cho