it%20Too%20Long...%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20At%20New%20Boeing%20Plant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20not%20have%20to%20wait%20too%20long%20for%20a%20Boeing%20aircraft%20that%20is%20designed%20and%20manufactured%20in%20the%20subcontinent%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20at%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20plane%20maker's%20engineering%20centre%20in%20Bengaluru%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Boeing%20India%20Engineering%20and%20Technology%20Centre%20(BIETC)%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20the%20company's%20largest%20facility%20outside%20of%20the%20US.%20It%20will%20focus%20on%20research%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20event%2C%20which%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20senior%20Boeing%20executives%20including%20Chief%20Operating%20Officer%20Stephanie%20Pope%2C%20PM%20Modi%20stressed%20the%20need%20to%20build%20an%20aircraft%20manufacturing%20ecosystem%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20that%20there%20is%20so%20much%20potential%20in%20India%2C%20we%20need%20to%20rapidly%20build%20an%20aircraft%20manufacturing%20ecosystem%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20proclaimed%20from%20the%20ramparts%20of%20the%20Red%20Fort%20-%20'this%20is%20the%20time%2C%20this%20is%20the%20right%20time'.%20It%20is%20also%20the%20opportune%20time%20for%20Boeing%20and%20other%20international%20companies%20to%20align%20their%20growth%20with%20Bharat's%20rapid%20progress.%20The%20commitment%20of%20140%20crore%20Indians%20is%20now%20focused%20on%20building%20a%20developed%20Bharat%20in%20the%20next%2025%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20such%20immense%20potential%20in%20Bharat%2C%20we%20must%20swiftly%20establish%20the%20aircraft%20manufacturing%20ecosystem.%20Bharat%20boasts%20a%20robust%20network%20of%20MSMEs%20and%20a%20vast%20talent%20pool.%20Coupled%20with%20a%20stable%20government%20and%20a%20policy%20approach%20that%20encourages%20'Make%20in%20India'%2C%20this%20creates%20a%20win-win%20situation%20for%20every%20sector.%20I%20believe%20that%20the%20people%20won't%20have%20to%20wait%20long%20for%20Boeing's%20first%20fully%20designed%20and%20manufactured%20aircraft%20in%20Bharat%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F5o3fil3s_pm-modi-boeings-engineering-and-tech-centre-bengaluru-ani_625x300_19_January_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBIETC%20was%20built%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%201%2C600%20crore%20on%20a%2043-acre%20plot%20at%20Hightech%20Defence%20and%20Aerospace%20Park%20in%20Devanahalli%2C%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Bengaluru.%20The%20facility%20is%20expected%20to%20become%20a%20cornerstone%20for%20partnerships%20with%20vibrant%20startups%2C%20and%20private%20and%20government%20ecosystem%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20did%20not%20give%20details%20on%20the%20number%20of%20people%20the%20new%20facility%20will%20employ.%20Boeing%20currently%20employs%20more%20than%206%2C000%20people%20in%20India%20across%20its%20various%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20launched%20the%20Boeing%20Sukanya%20Programme%20that%20the%20company%20said%20aims%20to%20support%20the%20entry%20of%20more%20girl%20children%20from%20across%20India%20into%20the%20country's%20growing%20aviation%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20will%20provide%20opportunities%20for%20girls%20and%20women%20from%20across%20India%20to%20learn%20critical%20skills%20in%20the%20science%2C%20technology%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20mathematics%20(STEM)%20fields%20and%20train%20for%20jobs%20in%20the%20aviation%20sector%2C%20Boeing%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20honoured%20and%20privileged%20to%20support%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20transformative%20vision%20for%20India%2C%20and%20we%20are%20grateful%20to%20have%20him%20dedicate%20the%20Boeing%20campus%20to%20foster%20aerospace%20innovation%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20L%20Calhoun%2C%20Boeing%20president%20and%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%20seen%20a%20surge%20in%20interest%20for%20its%20jets%20in%20India%2C%20currently%20the%20world's%20fastest-growing%20aviation%20market%2C%20with%20travel%20demand%20outstripping%20the%20supply%20of%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20aircraft%20manufacturer%20received%20orders%20for%20150%20737%20MAX%20narrow-body%20jets%20from%20Akasa%20Air%2C%20India's%20youngest%20carrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%20an%20alliance%20with%20Tata%20Group%20to%20produce%20AH-64%20Apache%20helicopter%20fuselages%20and%20737%20aircraft%20vertical%20fin%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Reuters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705682340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F0jebl6d_bengaluru-boeing-modi_625x300_19_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-wont-have-to-wait-too-long-what-pm-narendra-modi-said-at-new-boeing-plant-in-bengaluru-4894611%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20will%20not%20have%20to%20wait%20too%20long%20for%20a%20Boeing%20aircraft%20that%20is%20designed%20and%20manufactured%20in%20the%20subcontinent%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20at%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20plane%20maker's%20engineering%20centre%20in%20Bengaluru%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-wont-have-to-wait-too-long-what-pm-narendra-modi-said-at-new-boeing-plant-in-bengaluru-4894611%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-wont-have-to-wait-too-long-what-pm-narendra-modi-said-a