icopters%20were%20flying%20overhead%20and%20going%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20where%20the%20Iranian%20strike%20hit%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20know%20what%20had%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20Maulana%20Mohammad%20Sadiq%2C%2042%2C%20the%20prayer%20leader%20of%20a%20small%20seminary%20around%20five%20kilometres%20(three%20miles)%20from%20where%20a%20missile%20hit%2C%20told%20AFP%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVillagers%20feared%20that%20deteriorating%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20could%20lead%20to%20border%20closures%20and%20cut%20off%20residents%20from%20Iranian%20trade%2C%20which%20the%20area%20relies%20on%20for%20employment%20and%20food%20imports.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Iranians%20close%20the%20border%2C%20the%20people%20will%20starve%20and%20it%20will%20cause%20more%20militancy%20because%20youth%20will%20join%20the%20separatist%20organisations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%2055-year-old%20Haji%20Mohammad%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaluch%20separatists%20have%20been%20waging%20a%20low-level%20insurgency%20against%20Pakistani%20authorities%20from%20the%20largely%20ungoverned%2C%20impoverished%20region%20fighting%20for%20a%20better%20share%20of%20mineral%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERights%20groups%20say%20the%20military's%20crackdown%20on%20the%20insurgency%20has%20included%20widespread%20enforced%20disappearances%20and%20extrajudicial%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilitancy%20has%20also%20risen%20sharply%20along%20Pakistan's%20border%20with%20Afghanistan%20further%20north%2C%20after%20the%20Taliban's%20return%20to%20power%20there%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705681980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F52or6hjo_pakistan-strikes-iran_625x300_18_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.co