%20%26quot%3BIt's%20sincerely%20hoped%20that%20the%20India%20side%20would%20resume%20normal%20visa%20channels%20for%20Chinese%20citizens%20traveling%20to%20India%20ASAP%20to%20jointly%20promote%20mutual%20people-to-people%20and%20cultural%20exchanges%20between%20China%20%26amp%3B%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%202022%2C%20India%20suspended%20tourist%20visas%20for%20Chinese%20nationals%2C%20International%20Air%20Transport%20Association%20(IATA)%20said%20in%20a%20circular%20for%20its%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIATA%20issued%20a%20circular%20for%20its%20member%20carriers%20regarding%20entry%20into%20India%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTourist%20visas%20issued%20to%20nationals%20of%20China%20(People's%20Republic)%20are%20no%20longer%20valid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20reads%20that%20the%20nationals%20of%20Bhutan%2C%20India%2C%20Maldives%20and%20Nepal%2C%20passengers%20with%20a%20residence%20permit%20issued%20by%20India%2C%20passengers%20with%20visas%20or%20e-visa%20issued%20by%20India%20are%20allowed%20to%20enter%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20circular%2C%20passengers%20with%20an%20overseas%20citizen%20of%20India%20card%20or%20booklet%20like%20those%20who%20have%20a%20Persons%20of%20Indian%20Origin%20(PIO)%20card%20and%20those%20with%20a%20diplomatic%20passport%20are%20also%20allowed%20to%20enter%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IATA%20also%20said%20that%20tourist%20visas%20with%20a%20validity%20of%2010%20years%20are%20no%20longer%20valid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705679340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-04%2Findia-china-flags_650x400_61523324939.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-issued-1-8-lakh-visas-to-indian-citizens-in-2023-4894454%22%2C%2