20Saturday%20became%20the%20world's%20fifth%20country%20to%20put%20a%20spacecraft%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20as%20the%20space%20agency%20said%20its%20Smart%20Lander%20for%20Investigating%20Moon%20(SLIM)%20has%20made%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Japan%20Aerospace%20Exploration%20Agency%20has%20attempted%20the%20landing%20of%20the%20probe%20dubbed%20%26quot%3Bmoon%20sniper%26quot%3B%20within%20100%20metres%20(328%20feet)%20of%20target.%20It%20will%20take%20up%20to%20a%20month%20to%20verify%20if%20SLIM%20has%20achieved%20the%20precision%20goals%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705679220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F5h10gf6g_japan-moon-lander-_625x300_19_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapans-moon-sniper-lands-on-lunar-surface-first-for-country-4894323%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Japan%20on%20Saturday%20became%20the%20world's%20fifth%20country%20to%20put%20a%20spacecraft%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20as%20the%20space%20agency%20said%20its%20Smart%20Lander%20for%20Investigating%20Moon%20(SLIM)%20has%20made%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapans-moon-sniper-lands-on-lunar-surface-first-for-country-4894323%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapans-moon-sniper-lands-on-lunar-surface-first-for-country-4894323%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapans-moon-sniper-lands-on-lunar-surface-first-for-country-4894323%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Indian%20Police%20Force'%3A%20Rohit%20Shetty's%20Diatribe%20Against%20Muslims%2C%20Tempered%20With%20the%20'Good%20Muslim'%20Cliche%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19211320%2FEffect-72.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EVisualise%20this%3A%20a%20dozen%20cops%20storm%20the%20home%20of%20a%20working-class%20Muslim%20family.%20The%20top%20cop%20is%20barking%20orders%2C%20asking%20his%20subordinates%20to%20search%20every%20corner%20for%20any%20possible%20weapons%2C%20armed%20accomplices%2C%20or%20explosives.%20The%20family%20members%20can%20only%20look%20on%20with%20disbelief%20as%20they%E2%80%99re%20told%20their%20husbands%2C%20fathers%2C%20and%20brothers%20are%20%E2%80%98terrorists%E2%80%99.%20The%20cops%20accuse%20them%20of%20pretending.%20How%20does%20it%20play%20in%20India%20in%202024%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20world%20of%20the%20show%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20suspected%20characters%20%3Cem%3Eare%3C%2Fem%3E%20indeed%20terrorists%2C%20justifying%20the%20cops%20rudeness%20%E2%80%93%20does%20it%20make%20you%20uncomfortable%3F%20Even%20with%20the%20knowledge%20I%20was%20watching%20a%20web%20series%20by%20Rohit%20Shetty%20%E2%80%93%20known%20for%20his%20broad%20strokes%20because%20he%20makes%20%E2%80%98entertainers%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20I%20found%20myself%20shifting%20uneasily%20a%20bit.%20Especially%20at%20a%20time%20when%20political%20prisoners%20(many%20of%20whom%20happen%20to%20be%20Muslims)%20are%20awaiting%20trial%2C%20and%20their%20pleas%20for%20bail%20being%20rejected%20over%20several%20weeks%2C%20months%2C%20and%20years.%20Shetty%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20films%20with%20social%20relevance.%20He%20wants%20to%20pander.%20And%20if%20that%20means%20intensifying%20problematic%20stereotypes%2C%20then%20so%20be%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20Shetty%20isn%E2%80%99t%20merely%20satisfied%20with%20making%20money-churners%2C%20he%20also%20wants%20to%20appear%20as%20a%20conscientious%20man.%20So%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20his%20casual%20Islamophobia%20%E2%80%93%20he%E2%80%99ll%20throw%20in%20an%20upper-class%20Muslim%20cop%20called%20Kabir%20Malik%20(Sidharth%20Malhotra).%20His%20middle%20name%20could%20very%20well%20be%20Greater%20Kailash%20%E2%80%93%20such%20is%20the%20sophistication%20dripping%20from%20his%20Burberry%20shirts%2C%20aviators%20and%20hair%20that%20rarely%20looks%20out%20of%20place.%20With%20a%20Muslim%20cop%20dismissing%20%E2%80%98jihad%E2%80%99%20as%20ch*tiyapa%2C%20and%20lines%20like%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIslam%20tere%20baap%20ka%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%20(Do%20you%20own%20Islam%3F)%20%E2%80%93%20Shetty%20wants%20to%20have%20his%20cake%20and%20eat%20it%20too.%20He%20wants%20to%20showcase%20he%E2%80%99s%20aware%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20case%20of%20a%20few%20rotten%20apples%2C%20but%20also%20wants%20to%20do%20it%20while%20casting%20aspersions%20that%20most%20Muslims%20in%20India%20have%20to%20live%20with%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Shetty%E2%80%99s%20seven-part%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Police%20Force%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20seemingly%20ordinary%20Muslim%20family%20living%20in%20a%20locality%20called%20Ferozanagar%2C%20has%20a%20guest%20living%20with%20them%20called%20Haider%20(Mayankk%20Taandon).%20His%20real%20name%20is%20Zaraar%20(we%E2%80%99re%20later%20told)%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20the%20mastermind%20of%20serial%20blasts%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Delhi%20recently.%20Shetty%20could%E2%80%99ve%20left%20it%20at%20just%20this%20%E2%80%93%20after%20all%20a%20stranger%20living%20in%20the%20house%20could%20be%20anyone.%20But%20Shetty%20also%20plants%20an%20elder%20in%20this%20seemingly%20ordinary%20Muslim%20family%2C%20the%20patriarch%2C%20Saeed%20(Lalit%20Parimoo)%2C%20who%20is%20apparently%20a%20%E2%80%98sleeper%20agent%E2%80%99%2C%20helping%20Zaraar%20in%20his%20mission.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20dig%20deep%20to%20get%20to%20what%20Shetty%20is%20implying%3A%20most%20Muslim%20ghettos%20are%20embedded%20with%20terrorists%20and%20terrorist-sympathisers%20%E2%80%93%20a%20stance%20emphatically%20endorsed%20by%20we%20know%20who.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F6Jr4lNiK6XE%3Fsi%3DkDD4EveEyuK76iC0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Shetty%20has%20rarely%20been%20known%20for%20his%20nifty%20wit%20or%20nuanced%20observations.%20Like%20in%20%3Cem%3ESimmba%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2018)%2C%20his%20solution%20for%20rapes%20in%20society%20was%20to%20get%20muscular%20men%20to%20kill%20the%20alleged%20perpetrators.%20Due%20process%20be%20damned.%20Shetty%20is%20a%20huge%20supporter%20of%20the%20Indian%20police%20%E2%80%93%20considering%20his%20most%20lucrative%20projects%20have%20been%20woven%20around%20them%20(%3Cem%3ESingham%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ESimmba%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ESooryavanshi%3C%2Fem%3E).%20Therefore%2C%20he%20takes%20the%20convenient%20route%20of%20putting%20the%20department%20on%20a%20pedestal%2C%20implying%3A%20the%20department%20is%20not%20corrupt%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20a%20few%20cops.%20Just%20like%20the%20Muslims%20in%20his%20films%2Fshow%20%E2%80%93%20Shetty%20tries%20a%20balancing%20act%2C%20like%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20chemistry%20equation.%20For%20every%20five%20%E2%80%98bad%20Muslim%E2%80%99%20characters%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Police%20Forc%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Ee%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethere%E2%80%99s%20a%20sincere%2C%20skull%20cap-wearing%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Esaccha%20musalmaan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%20For%20every%20radical%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20parent%20who%20won%E2%80%99t%20accept%20the%20body%20of%20a%20slain%20terrorist.%20The%20parent%20will%20also%20deliver%20a%20melodramatic%20monologue%20about%20how%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20bigger%20betrayal%20than%20betraying%20one%E2%80%99s%20nation.%20The%20upper-class%20Muslim%20will%20slap%20a%20suspected%20terrorist%20in%20jail%2C%20saying%20how%20a%20few%20like%20them%20give%20a%20bad%20name%20to%20a%20whole%20%3Cem%3Eqaum%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20often%20makes%20me%20wonder%2C%20the%20role%20such%20films%2Fshows%20play%20in%20contributing%20to%20and%20even%20escalating%20paranoia%20on%20a%20national%20scale.%20Or%20is%20it%20the%20other%20way%20round%2C%20such%20shows%20are%20watched%20on%20a%20national%20scale%20because%20of%20pre-existing%20paranoia.%20What%20it%20surely%20does%20is%20feed%20off%20each%20other.%20For%20filmmakers%20like%20Rohit%20Shetty%2C%20who%20are%20watched%20by%20crores%20of%20people%2C%20how%20responsible%20is%20that%3F%20Especially%20at%20a%20time%20when%20public%20discourse%20is%20plummeting%20fiercely%20and%20pop%20culture%20seems%20to%20be%20emulating%20widespread%20sentiments.%20On%20some%20level%2C%20Vivek%20Ranjan%20Agnihotri%20(of%20%3Cem%3EKashmir%20Files%3C%2Fem%3E%20fame)%20and%20Sudipto%20Sen%20(of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kerala%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E%20fame)%20seem%20more%20honest%2C%20compared%20to%20Shetty.%20At%20least%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20try%20to%20obfuscate%20their%20derision%20for%20Muslims.%20It%E2%80%99s%20out%20there.%20Shetty%20on%20his%20part%20thinks%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%20planting%20a%20few%20decent%20Muslims%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20somehow%20better%20than%20Agnihotri%20and%20Sen.%20A%20case%20could%20be%20made%20for%20why%20he%E2%80%99s%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20other%20problems%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Police%20Force%3C%2Fem%3E%20too.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20even%20getting%20into%20the%20thinly-plotted%20missions%2C%20the%20garbage%20VFX%20to%20showcase%20terror%20attacks%2C%20the%20persistent%20slo-mo%20or%20the%20pedestrian%20acting%20(a%20constant%20in%20most%20of%20Shetty%E2%80%99s%20films)%2C%20where%20volume%20means%20everything.%20As%20the%20cops%20go%20about%20their%20%E2%80%98covert%20operations%E2%80%99%2C%20Shetty%20spends%20literally%20zero%20minutes%20showing%20the%20planning%20stages%20of%20any%20of%20these%20operations.%20In%20a%20show%20with%20a%20runtime%20of%20nearly%20four%20hours%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20ever%20hear%20any%20character%20raising%20any%20eyebrow%20about%20the%20collateral%20damage%20or%20the%20death%20of%20the%20lower-ranked%20cops.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20when%20a%20main%20character%20dies%20that%20Shetty%20summons%20the%20violins%20and%20tears.%20Almost%20as%20if%20these%20cops%20operate%20on%20Virender%20Sehwag%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Csee%20ball%2C%20hit%20ball%E2%80%9D%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20climax%2C%20where%20the%20cops%20are%20trying%20to%20arrest%20someone%20on%20foreign%20soil%20(where%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20jurisdiction)%2C%20Shetty%20makes%20the%20most%20indiscreet%20choice%20possible.%20He%20announces%20his%20star%20in%20a%20slow-motion%20shot%2C%20bracing%20himself%20for%20an%20easily%20avoidable%20public%20shoot-out.%20Like%20he%20usually%20does%2C%20Shetty%20chooses%20style%20over%20logic.%20There%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20songs%20(shot%20by%20Sneha%20Shetty%20Kohli)%20that%20are%20in%20the%20show%2C%20which%20makes%20me%20wonder%20if%20this%20was%20conceived%20as%20a%20film%20and%20later%20repurposed%20as%20a%20show%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20more%20than%20clear%20that%20Shetty%20has%20no%20understanding%20of%20the%20rhythm%20of%20a%20web%20series.%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20venture%20a%20guess%20that%20Shetty%20thinks%20of%20web%20series%20as%20merely%20films%20with%20a%20longer%20duration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20better%20or%20worse%2C%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Police%20Force%3C%2Fem%3E%20plays%20out%20like%20a%20%E2%80%98mindless%E2%80%99%20Rohit%20Shetty%20film.%20Not%20one%20extra%20grey%20cell%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20spent%20adjusting%20one%E2%80%99s%20style%20around%20a%20new%20format.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20good%20chance%20that%20such%20a%20show%20%E2%80%93%20which%20might%20sound%20like%20music%20to%20the%20champions%20of%20WhatsApp%20%E2%80%93%20might%20go%20on%20to%20do%20well.%20And%20if%20that%20happens%2C%20we%20might%20have%20to%20ask%20him%20about%20his%20social%20responsibility%20as%20a%20filmmaker.%20Shetty%20probably%20realises%20the%20consequences%20of%20his%20deliberate%20choices%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20chooses%20to%20be%20blinded%20by%20success%20and%20accolades.%20Or%20he%E2%80%99s%20comfortable%20instigating%20the%20enmity%20towards%20a%20group%2C%20his%20fellow%20citizens%2C%20to%20keep%20the%20fire%20in%20his%20kitchen%20burning.%20Either%20way%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20terrible%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20film%20ensures%20that%20he%20will%20be%20known%20as%20yet%20another%20filmmaker%20who%20profited%20from%20helping%20build%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20fear.%20Especially%20in%20an%20election%20year.%20We%20see%20you%2C%20Mr%20Shetty.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705679205000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19211320%2FEffect-72.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Findian-police-force-rohit-shettys-diatribe-against-muslims-tempered-with-the-good-muslim-cliche%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20director%2C%20known%20for%20his%20violent%2C%20high-decibel%20cop%20films%20can%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20come%20to%20grips%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20web-series.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Findian-police-force-rohit-shettys-diatribe-against-muslims-tempered-with-the-good-muslim-cliche%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seer%20Pulls%20Lord%20Ram%20Chariot%20With%20His%20Hair%20Over%20566%20Km%20To%20Ayodhya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20devotees%20countdown%20to%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%2C%20many%20are%20showing%20their%20devotion%20to%20Lord%20Ram%20in%20different%20ways.%20A%20seer%20from%20Damoh%20in%20Madhya