w.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fanant-raj-raises-rs-500-cr-via-issue-of-shares-to-institutional-investors-124011900712_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20a%20Small%20Village%20in%20Bengal%2C%20a%20Celebration%20that%20Combines%20Various%20Religious%20Traditions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19170405%2FScreenshot-2024-01-19-at-5.03.10%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20year%20between%20January%2014%20and%2016%2C%20Joydev%20Kenduli%20%E2%80%93%2013%20kilometres%20from%20Illambazar%20in%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Birbhum%20district%20and%20a%20small%20village%20situated%20at%20the%20banks%20of%20Ajay%20river%20%E2%80%93%20receives%20people%20from%20across%20the%20state%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20occasion%20is%20the%20Joydev%20Mela%20named%20after%2012%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20poet-saint%20who%20wrote%20the%20%3Cem%3EGita%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EGovinda%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Sanskrit.%20Though%20there%20is%20some%20uncertainty%20in%20academic%20circles%20about%20the%20exact%20origins%20of%20Joydev%20%E2%80%93%20also%20spelled%20Jayadev%2C%20according%20to%20north%20Indian%20pronunciation%20%E2%80%93%20but%20locals%20people%20believe%20that%20he%20was%20born%2C%20lived%20and%20wrote%20the%20%3Cem%3EGita%20Govinda%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20Joydev%20Kenduli.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMakar%20Sankranti%2C%20usually%20celebrated%20on%20January%2015%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20Joydev%E2%80%99s%20birth%20anniversary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20like%20to%20recount%20a%20story%20that%20on%20this%20day%2C%20Joydev%20went%20to%20bathe%20in%20the%20Ajay%20river.%20He%20was%20struggling%20with%20the%20last%20two%20verses%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EGita%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EGovinda%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3Cspan%3EWhen%20he%20returned%20home%20and%20asked%20his%20wife%20to%20serve%20him%20food%2C%20she%20responded%20with%20surprise.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20said%20you%20finished%20the%20last%20two%20verses%20of%20the%20poem%20after%20returning%20from%20your%20bath%20and%20ate%20the%20food%20I%20served%20you.%20Why%20are%20you%20asking%20for%20food%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJoydev%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Krishna%20who%20had%20finished%20the%20verses%20for%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20particular%20lore%20also%20assures%20Joydev%20Kenduli%20of%20its%20sacred%20geography.%20It%20is%20also%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20the%20harvest%20festival%20celebrated%20across%20cultures%20in%20India%20coincides%20with%20the%20Joydev%20Mela.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20old%20temple%20of%20Radha%20Madhav%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20village.%20Locals%20believe%20that%20Joydev%20himself%20worshiped%20Radha%20Madhav%20at%20this%20temple%2C%20making%20this%20place%20a%20pilgrimage%20site%20for%20Bengal%20Vaishnavism%20and%20followers%20of%20the%20Bhakti%20tradition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20also%20strongly%20believe%20that%20they%20will%20be%20freed%20from%20their%20sins%20if%20they%20take%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Ajay%20river%20on%20the%2015%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20January%20before%20noon.%20However%2C%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years%20the%20water%20flow%20in%20the%20Ajay%20has%20been%20weak.%20Thus%20water%20from%20the%20Mayurakshi%20river%2C%20stored%20in%20the%20Tilpara%20reservoir%2C%20is%20released%20two%20days%20before%20the%20festival.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVarious%20shops%20sell%20agricultural%20tools%2C%20along%20with%20kitchen%20and%20household%20items.%20It%20is%20also%20strongly%20believed%20that%20one%20needs%20to%20buy%20bananas%20while%20returning%20home%20from%20the%20Mela!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20can%20also%20sight%20political%20flags%20of%20various%20parties%20at%20the%20fair%20grounds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20noticeable%20aspects%20of%20the%20area%20is%20that%20there%20are%2050%20permanent%20ashrams%20housing%20various%20gurus%20(popularly%20called%20%E2%80%98maharaja%E2%80%99)%2C%20living%20and%20dead.%20More%20than%20280%20makeshift%20%3Cem%3Eakharas%3C%2Fem%3E%20sprout%20during%20the%20three%20days%20of%20the%20Mela.%20Here%2C%20all%20night%2C%20bhajans%2C%20katha%20pravachans%20and%20Baul%20performances%20take%20place.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDevotees%20reach%20the%20area%20in%20large%20numbers%20for%20these%20shows.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20497px)%2085vw%2C%20497px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19170421%2FScreenshot-2024-01-19-at-5.03.02%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22497%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19170421%2FScreenshot-2024-01-19-at-5.03.02%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%20868w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19170421%2FScreenshot-2024-01-19-at-5.03.02%25E2%2580%25AFPM-269x300.png%20269w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693698%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22554%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDevotees%20at%20the%20Joydev%20Kenduli%20Mela.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20of%20ashrams%20and%20akharas%20hire%20religious%20preachers%20and%20performers%20who%20are%20specialised%20in%20the%20Rasa%20Leela%2C%20to%20entertain%20the%20devotees%20that%20choose%20to%20spend%20the%20night.%20The%20religious%20performers%20often%20come%20in%20groups.%20Every%20akhara%20is%20fitted%20with%20loudspeakers%20and%20colourful%20posters%20to%20advertise%20the%20preachers%20who%20will%20perform.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20very%20common%20to%20find%20women%20preachers%20and%20performers%20in%20lead%20roles.%20Many%20performers%20are%20from%20communities%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes.%20Often%2C%20when%20preachers%20perform%2C%20the%20devotees%20often%20stand%20up%20to%20dance%20and%20chant%20slogans%20in%20praise%20of%20the%20gods.%20Thus%2C%20they%20become%20one%20with%20the%20performance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tradition%20of%20families%20in%20Bengal%20associating%20themselves%20with%20a%20guru%20and%20guruma%20is%20popular.%20Sometimes%20the%20members%20of%20the%20family%20also%20have%20the%20liberty%20to%20choose%20from%20different%20gurus.%20The%20guru%20acts%20as%20a%20spiritual%20guide%20and%20it%20is%20as%20tribute%20to%20them%20that%20the%20songs%20are%20primarily%20sung.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20mix%20of%20traditions%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20common%20knowledge%20that%20Shakti%20(female%20worship)%20and%20tantric%20traditions%20are%20prevalent%20in%20the%20eastern%20states%20of%20India%2C%20especially%20in%20Bengal.%20A%20close%20look%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3ECharyapada%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20collection%20of%20mystical%20poems%20from%20the%208-12%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century)%20tells%20us%20that%20there%20was%20an%20intermix%20of%20Buddhism%20(particularly%20Vajrayana%20Buddhism)%20and%20female%20goddess%20worship.%20The%2012%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20period%20when%20Buddhism%20was%20on%20the%20decline%20in%20Indian%20sub-continent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%2012%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%2C%20Joydev%2C%20and%20in%20the%2015%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%2C%20Chaitanya%20Mahaprabhu%20became%20pioneering%20figures%20who%20contributed%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20Bengal%20Vaishnavism.%20Myths%20and%20stories%20of%20Krishna%20interacting%20with%20these%20two%20devotees%20keep%20their%20legacy%20alive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERadha%2C%20too%2C%20has%20been%20a%20central%20figure%20in%20this%20Bhakti%20tradition%20and%20the%20figure%20preaches%20that%20with%20absolute%20love%20and%20devotion%20one%20can%20reach%20Krishna%2C%20a%20form%20of%20the%20supreme%20being%2C%20Vishnu.%20These%20philosophies%2C%20rituals%2C%20and%20methods%20of%20reaching%20out%20to%20god%20in%20Bengal%20Vaishnavism%20are%20unique%20and%20in%20contrast%20to%20organised%20religion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBirbhum%20district%20where%20Joydev%20Mela%20is%20held%2C%20is%20considered%20Baul%20Desh%20or%20country%20of%20the%20Bauls.%20Bauls%20are%20mystics%20who%20live%20lives%20of%20ascetics%20and%20preach%20humanity%2C%20minimalism%20and%20living%20with%20the%20nature.%20Bauls%2C%20in%20their%20music%2C%20often%20evoke%20the%20traditions%20of%20Vaishnavism%2C%20Sufism%20and%20Buddhism.%20There%20are%20many%20Bauls%20who%20also%20practice%20Islam%20as%20their%20religion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Joydev%20Mela%20is%20also%20popularly%20known%20as%20Baul%20Mela%20and%20various%20religious%20traditions%20amalgamate%20there%20to%20make%20the%20Mela%20thriving%2C%20interesting%20and%20inclusive.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcademics%20may%20classify%20these%20traditions%20as%20different%20from%20each%20other%2C%20but%20for%20those%20visiting%20Joydev%20Mela%20all%20the%20traditions%20are%20one%20in%20giving%20hope.%20The%20mix%20of%20various%20religious%20traditions%20mirrors%20the%20religious%20plurality%20that%20has%20historically%20been%20present%20in%20India%20and%20gives%20a%20definition%20of%20the%20religious%20assimilation%2C%20appropriation%20and%20integration%20of%20one%20tradition%20with%20the%20other.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ESipoy%20Sarveswar%20and%20M.P.%20Terence%20Samuel%20teach%20anthropology%2C%20philosophy%20and%20comparative%20religion%20at%20Visva-Bharati%2C%20Shantiniketan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20authors%20acknowledge%20the%20assistance%20provided%20by%20their%20students%20Sourav%20Garain%20(and%20his%20family)%2C%20Binoy%20Das%2C%20and%20Sheikh%20Nijamatulla.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705667615000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19170405%2FScreenshot-2024-01-19-at-5.03.10%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fbengal-joydev-gita-govinda-religion%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Joydev%20Mela%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20traditions%2C%20religious%20practices%2C%20mysticism%20and%20music.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fbengal-joydev-gita-govinda-religion%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Important%20are%20Social%20Media%20Influencers%20in%20Indian%20Elections%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F05191853%2FIMG_0575.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%202%2C%202023%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20met%20Ankit%20Baiyanpuria%2C%20a%20social%20media%20fitness%20influencer%20from%20Haryana.%20He%20joined%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Eshramdaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20program%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Swachhata%20Hi%20Seva%E2%80%99%20campaign.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20also%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20him%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20and%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20as%20the%20nation%20focuses%20on%20Swachhata%2C%20Ankit%20Baiyanpuriya%20and%20I%20did%20the%20same!%20Beyond%20just%20cleanliness%2C%20we%20blended%20fitness%20and%20well-being%20also%20into%20the%20mix.%20It%20is%20all%20about%20that%20Swachh%20and%20Swasth%20Bharat%20vibe!%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20post%20highlights%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20social%20media%20influencers%20who%20are%20crucial%20in%20Indian%20elections%20due%20to%20their%20wide%20reach%2C%20accessibility%2C%20and%20ability%20to%20engage%20diverse%20demographics%2C%20especially%20the%20youth.%20They%20play%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20digital%20campaigning%2C%20amplifying%20political%20messages%2C%20and%20providing%20real-time%20coverage.%20These%20influencers%20contribute%20to%20image%20building%20through%20endorsements%20and%20also%20shape%20public%20opinions%20during%20election%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20a%20social%20media%20influencer%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20social%20media%20influencer%20is%20an%20individual%20who%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20sway%20their%20audience%20towards%20purchasing%20the%20products%20or%20services%20they%20endorse.%20Based%20on%20their%20followers%20they%20are%20broadly%20categorised%20into%20four%20types.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20%E2%80%98nano%E2%80%99%20influencers%2C%20with%200-10%2C000%20followers%2C%20are%20cost-effective%20and%20ideal%20for%20small%20to%20medium-sized%20businesses%20with%20limited%20budgets.%20They%20often%20have%20a%20highly%20engaged%20following%2C%20making%20their%20recommendations%20more%20trustworthy.%20Nano%20influencers%20usually%20specialise%20in%20specific%20topics%2C%20providing%20targeted%20exposure%20for%20any%20services.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%2C%20micro%20influencers%2C%20having%2010%2C000-100%2C000%20followers%2C%20are%20suitable%20for%20any%20brand%20aiming%20to%20reach%20new%20engaged%20audiences.%20They%20offer%20cost-effective%20collaboration%20with%20clients%20and%20their%20audience%E2%80%99s%20needs.%20Micro-influencers%20are%20particularly%20effective%20for%20brand%20awareness%20campaigns.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThird%2C%20macro%20influencers%2C%20ranging%20from%201-10%20lakh%20followers%2C%20are%20well-suited%20for%20brands%20seeking%20to%20reach%20large%20audiences.%20They%20often%20engage%20their%20audience%20across%20multiple%20platforms%20and%20may%20have%20additional%20platforms%20like%20a%20website%20or%20podcast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-money-spent-on-union-ministers-interviews-with-social-media-influencers-govt-tells-parliament%5C%22%3ENo%20Money%20Spent%20on%20Union%20Ministers%E2%80%99%20Interviews%20With%20Social%20Media%20Influencers%2C%20Govt%20Tells%20Parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFourth%2C%20mega%20influencers%2C%20with%20more%20than%2010%20lakh%20followers%2C%20are%20employed%20for%20campaigns%20focused%20on%20awareness%20and%20sales%20with%20substantial%20budgets.%20They%20offer%20the%20opportunity%20to%20reach%20large%20audiences%20and%20are%20suitable%20for%20major%20product%20launches%20or%20significant%20events.%20Mega%20influencers%20typically%20have%20well-established%20credibility%20and%20create%20high-quality%2C%20professional%20content.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESocial%20media%20influencer%20political%20marketing%20is%20pivotal%20in%20shaping%20narratives%20and%20engaging%20with%20diverse%20voters.%20Political%20parties%20collaborate%20with%20influencers%20of%20different%20types%20based%20on%20their%20campaign%20goals%20and%20budgets.%20Nano%20and%20micro-influencers%20connect%20with%20local%20communities%2C%20while%20macro%20and%20mega-influencers%20spread%20messages%20to%20a%20vast%20audience.%20Social%20media%20influencers%E2%80%99%20digital%20trust%20and%20belongingness%20with%20their%20audience%20compel%20politicians%20and%20political%20parties%20to%20visit%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%202024%20general%20election%20draws%20near%2C%20social%20media%20influencers%20are%20in%20high%20demand%20and%20are%20being%20actively%20pursued%20to%20target%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20692%20million%2B%20online%20population.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20organised%20meetings%20with%20influencers%20across%20various%20regions%2C%20recognising%20their%20role%20in%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20success.%20Influencers%2C%20both%20big%20ones%20with%20millions%20of%20followers%20and%20smaller%20ones%20with%20specific%20audiences%2C%20are%20not%20only%20being%20pursued%20by%20the%20BJP%20but%20also%20by%20other%20political%20parties.%20These%20parties%20are%20ready%20to%20invest%20significantly%20to%20use%20their%20popularity%20for%20election%20campaigns.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20National%20Congress%20is%20not%20behind%20in%20this%20process.%20The%20party%20used%20them%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra.%20Another%20big%20step%20was%20taken%20by%20former%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20who%20launched%20the%20%E2%80%98Jan%20Samman%E2%80%99%20video%20contest%20aimed%20at%20promoting%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fquestions-over-financing-of-union-ministers-interviews-with-youtube-influencers%5C%22%3EQuestions%20Over%20Financing%20of%20Union%20Ministers%E2%80%99%20Interviews%20With%20YouTube%20Influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20contest%20encouraged%20participants%20to%20create%20short%20videos%20highlighting%20the%20impact%20of%20various%20welfare%20initiatives.%20Contestants%20had%20to%20share%2030%20to%20120-second%20videos%20on%20two%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20Facebook%2C%20Twitter%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20YouTube%20with%20the%20hashtag%20%23JanSammanJaiRajasthan.%20Winners%20were%20given%20cash%20prizes%20totalling%20Rs%202.75%20lakhs.%20The%20scheme%20promoted%20youth%20and%20social%20media%20influencers%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20Indian%20elections%2C%20influencers%2C%20who%20serve%20as%20both%20entertainers%20and%20political%20commentators%2C%20wield%20significant%20influence%20in%20connecting%20with%20diverse%20audiences%20and%20shaping%20political%20perspectives.%20These%20influencers%20generate%20substantial%20income%20by%20endorsing%20political%20messages%20and%20sharing%20political%20content.%20However%2C%20the%20promotional%20activities%20conducted%20by%20them%20often%20lack%20complete%20transparency.%20Some%20influencers%20express%20apprehension%20about%20facing%20criticism%20or%20negative%20feedback%20from%20political%20parties.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20imperative%20to%20establish%20mechanisms%20for%20ensuring%20the%20accountability%20of%20social%20media%20influencers%20in%20India.%20To%20make%20them%20more%20accountable%2C%20the%20country%20needs%20a%20multifaceted%20approach%20involving%20regulatory%20frameworks%2C%20self-regulation%2C%20and%20public%20awareness%20initiatives.%20The%20government%20needs%20to%20establish%20explicit%20guidelines%20and%20standards%20to%20ensure%20their%20ethical%20conduct.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EDr%20Nikhil%20Kumar%20Singhmar%20is%20an%20author%20and%20social%20media%20consultant%20in%20India.%20He%20holds%20a%20PhD%20in%20social%20media%20politics%20in%20India%20from%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University.%20His%20areas%20of%20interest%20include%20the%20discourse%20and%20narrative%20analysis%20associated%20with%20social%20media%2C%20election%20strategies%20and%20data%20analysis.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20author%20of%20%E2%80%9CAam%20Aadmi%20Party%3A%20Vichardhara%20aur%20Delhi%20Model.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3