overnment%E2%80%99s%20uncaring%20attitude%20to%20the%20public.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40RahulGandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FBharatJodoNyayYatra%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23BharatJodoNyayYatra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20clear%20the%20suffering%20of%20the%20people%20is%20not%20the%20suffering%20of%20this%20Government.%20Crores%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAoJsUDEG1H%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAoJsUDEG1H%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2702g5lEGx%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F2702g5lEGx%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20(%40ShashiTharoor)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FShashiTharoor%2Fstatus%2F1747838139446841803%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exchange%20of%20words%20first%20started%20when%20Tharoor%20in%20a%20series%20of%20tweets%20on%20January%2016%2C%20called%20the%20flight%20disruptions%20a%20%E2%80%9CModi%20Govt-made%20disaster%2C%20a%20result%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%E2%80%99s%20neglect%20and%20incompetence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttaching%20links%20to%20news%20articles%2C%20Tharoor%20said%20that%20in%20in%202008%2C%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%2C%20Delhi%20IGI%20Airport%20got%20a%20brand-new%20CAT%20III-B%20compliant%20runway-that%20allows%20pilots%20to%20land%20even%20when%20there%20is%20fog%20or%20low%20visibility%20of%2050%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20total%2C%20Delhi%20has%204%20runways%2C%202%20of%20which%20are%20CAT%20III-B%20compliant.%20In%20all%20its%20wisdom%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20began%20maintenance%20work%20on%20one%20of%20the%20two%20CAT%20III-B%20runways%20in%20September%202023%2C%20fully%20aware%20that%20it%20would%20not%20be%20ready%20for%20the%20winter!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20making%20matters%20worse%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20crane%20from%20some%20other%20construction%20work%20was%20blocking%20operation%20of%20CAT%20III-B%20on%20one%20runway%2C%20even%20after%20repairs%20were%20complete.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20pilots%20must%20be%20trained%20in%20CAT%20III-B%20landing%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20and%20the%20DGCA%20failed%20to%20ensure%20that%20airlines%20have%20sufficiently%20trained%20pilots%20and%20that%20pilots%20flying%20to%20Delhi%20during%20fog%20conditions%20were%20CAT%20III-B%20trained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20the%20civil%20aviation%20ministry%20had%20said%20that%20the%20visibility%20was%20below%2050%20metres%20so%20CAT%20III-B%20would%20not%20have%20been%20enough%2C%20he%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20not%20planning%20a%20single%20CAT%20III-C%20runway%2C%20which%20can%20land%20in%20zero%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20accused%20the%20ministry%20and%20the%20DGCA%20of%20not%20ensuring%20passenger%20rights%20that%20were%20put%20in%20place%20in%202010%20in%20case%20of%20flight%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20years%2C%20airlines%20have%20violated%20rules%20%E2%80%93%20passengers%20with%20tickets%20denied%20boarding%2C%20compensation%20not%20provided%20after%20delays%2C%20etc.%20DGCA%20%E2%80%98hauls%20them%20up%E2%80%99%20for%20publicity%2C%20but%20either%20takes%20no%20action%20or%20imposes%20fines%20of%20token%20amounts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20all%20this%20has%20resulted%20in%20chaos%20at%20airports%20which%20is%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20one%20of%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20chronic%20mismanagement%E2%80%9D%20and%20thanked%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20war%20room%20for%20doing%20the%20research%20behind%20his%20tweets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20January%2017%2C%20Scindia%20in%20