g%20that%20there%20had%20been%20some%20successful%20attempts%20to%20curb%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftaxes%2Ft-19021286%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Etax%20evasion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20large%20corporations%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20130%20countries%2C%20which%20together%20account%20for%2090%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20economic%20output%2C%20had%20also%20agreed%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fworld-leaders-hail-agreement-on-global-corporate-tax-rate%2Fa-59454797%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eminimum%2015%25%20tax%20rate%20for%20companies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20in%20so%20doing%20were%20trying%20to%20prevent%20companies%20from%20just%20moving%20onto%20other%20countries%20with%20better%20tax%20rates.%20Last%20year%2C%20several%20EU%20lawmakers%20proposed%20a%20similar%20global%20minimum%20tax%20on%20extremely%20high%20private%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Bach%20doubted%20that%20there%20would%20be%20any%20developments%20on%20this%20front%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20and%20this%20was%20partly%20to%20do%20with%20the%20general%20shift%20to%20the%20right%20across%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20hardly%20any%20left-wing%20majorities%20left%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20when%20it%20came%20to%20tax%20measures%2C%20it%20was%20important%20to%20have%20conservative%20and%20liberal%20parties%20on%20board%2C%20but%20these%20were%20inherently%20more%20business-friendly.%20He%20said%20that%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgermany%2Ft-17871182%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGermany%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0nothing%20would%20happen%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Ceven%20more%20difficult%20to%20coordinate%20something%20like%20this%20on%20an%20international%20scale.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fafricas-crises-fall-out-of-focus-as-global-attention-drifts%2Fa-67965128%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EDW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705654525000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fa-group-of-billionaires-and-millionaires-have-called-on-world-leaders-at-the-world-economic-forum-to-fight-social-inequality-by-taxing-the-rich-but-there-is-political-resistance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fa-group-of-billionaires-and-millionaires-have-called-on-world-leaders-at-the-world-economic-forum-to-fight-social-inequality-by-taxing-the-rich-but-there-is-political-resistance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aadhaar%20Card%20No%20Longer%20Acceptable%20as%20Proof%20of%20Date%20of%20Birth%3A%20EPFO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F09105721%2FAadhaar.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Employees%E2%80%99%20Provident%20Fund%20Organisation%20(EPFO)%20will%20no%20longer%20accept%20Aadhaar%20Card%20as%20proof%20of%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20the%20retirement%20fund%20body%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20(January%2016).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20has%20been%20made%20with%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20Central%20Provident%20Fund%20Commissioner%20(CPFC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20documents%20will%20be%20considered%20as%20valid%20proof%20of%20date%20of%20birth%20by%20the%20EPFO%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMarksheet%20issued%20by%20any%20recognised%20government%20board%20or%20university%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESchool%20Leaving%20Certificate%20(SLC)%2FSchool%20Transfer%20Certificate%20(TC)%2FSSC%20certificate%20with%C2%A0name%20and%20date%20of%20birth%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECertificate%20based%20on%20the%20service%20records%3C%2Fli%