erindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fsustainable-nature-retreat-10-1705578196-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338530%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETrails%20are%20a%20great%20opportunity%20to%20spot%20different%20birds%20and%20wildlife%20in%20the%20area%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Luv%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20grandfather%20was%20also%20instrumental%20in%20guiding%20Luv%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297379%2Fcouple-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econstructing%20the%20greywater%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20takes%20the%20wastewater%2C%20filters%20it%2C%20and%20channels%20it%20into%20the%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20took%20his%20advice%20seriously%2C%E2%80%9D%20Luv%20says.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20the%20last%20batch%20of%20people%20trained%20by%20the%20British%20and%20joined%20the%20Indian%20Forest%20Institute%20in%20Coimbatore%20in%201945.%20He%20was%20among%20the%20first%20trained%20people%20who%20joined%20the%20Government%20of%20Rajasthan%20Forest%20Department%20in%20the%20capacity%20of%20a%20ranger%20and%20helped%20set%20up%20Ranthambore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuv%20recalls%20the%20day%20his%20grandfather%20was%20on%20site%20and%20Luv%20was%20planning%20to%20clear%20out%20the%20garden%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwell-manicured%20lawn%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20shared%20a%20lesson%20with%20me%20that%20I%20still%20follow.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20look%20for%20dry%20leaves%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20ground.%20These%2C%20he%20said%2C%20were%20indicators%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332749%2Fex-banker-sunando-sen-built-tanhau-sustainable-himalayan-homestay-corbett-restore-wildlife%